42
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:34,240
Let go of my mom!

43
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,680
What are you doing?

44
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,160
Who are you people?

45
00:03:05,440 --> 00:03:07,040
Breaking into my home, what do you want?

46
00:03:14,700 --> 00:03:15,640
You don't recognize me?

47
