85
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:09,240
If you want something, come at me.

86
00:05:10,880 --> 00:05:11,880
Stay away from my sister.

87
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:15,480
Make the call to drop out of school.

88
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:19,120
From now on, you'll do what I say.

89
00:05:29,950 --> 00:05:30,900
You're smart.

90
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:33,160
You should know what you're worth.

91
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:35,080
If you just follow orders,

92
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:36,960
I'll naturally

93
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,360
let your family go.

94
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,200
What value do I have?

95
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,280
Of course you have.

96
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:48,600
It's just a pity

97
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:52,760
you'll never wear
that school uniform again.

98
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:08,980
Sis.

99
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:09,880
Sis, you're awake.

100
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,760
Come on.

101
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,320
What's wrong with me?

102
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:20,480
The cut on your hand got infected.

103
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,880
You've had a high fever
and been out cold for days.

104
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:25,960
Sis,

105
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,520
I really need to say this to you.

106
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,800
Don't mess around outside every day.

107
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:34,640
You're Yixiao's secretary now.

108
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:37,040
Even if you don't care about yourself,

109
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,480
at least don't embarrass him.

110
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:40,000
Embarrass?

111
00:06:41,740 --> 00:06:43,020
Then why do you think Gu Yixiao

112
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:44,680
keeps letting his secretary

113
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:45,880
fall into such a messy state

114
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:46,920
and lose all self-respect?

115
00:06:46,930 --> 00:06:48,960
You're saying Yixiao's
not a good guy, right?

116
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,480
I'm grown now.

117
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,440
I can see things clearly
with my own eyes.

118
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,880
Sis,

119
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:05,240
I don't know what happened
between you and Yixiao.

120
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,240
But all these years

121
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:09,240
he's really been good to us.

122
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,240
I honestly like him a lot.

123
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,160
You'd also want me

124
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,400
to find happiness, right?

125
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,720
You want to see me?

126
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:50,400
You told her to come to my room?

127
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,720
I didn't know that Wang Yaqin...

128
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:57,080
Don't mention her name.

129
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:03,360
Sorry.

130
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:12,920
Yixiao,

131
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,280
these past few years,

132
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,400
your attitude toward Ye Xingwan

133
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,600
has changed a lot.

134
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,200
Yixiao.

135
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:39,780
(Wang Qi: Find out?
Is my dad's death related to him?)

136
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,240
I'm begging you.

137
00:08:54,300 --> 00:08:56,140
We haven't eaten or had water
for three days.

138
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,720
My dad can't hold on much longer.

139
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,040
(Gu's father)

140
00:08:59,040 --> 00:09:00,800
(Young Gu Yixiao)
I'll do whatever you ask.

141
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,400
Deliver this package

142
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,800
to the warehouse at Pier 19.

143
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:07,680
Once you get it done,

144
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:10,800
all past debts will be cleared.

145
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:23,240
If there is even the slightest damage

146
00:09:23,520 --> 00:09:25,400
to anything in here,

147
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,400
I'll make sure your dad

148
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,960
ends up in the sea feeding sharks.

149
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:14,510
♪The fragility stripped away by you♪

150
00:10:15,030 --> 00:10:17,990
♪Keeps dragging me down endlessly♪

151
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:22,300
♪If not once devoured by blazing flames♪

152
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:25,400
♪Who would ever understand
this baptism by fire♪

153
00:10:25,680 --> 00:10:28,590
♪You betrayed me so decisively♪

154
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:32,020
♪With indifference laid bare♪

155
00:10:32,620 --> 00:10:35,610
♪It taught me to stay silent first♪

156
00:10:35,610 --> 00:10:39,120
♪So the explosion would be deafening♪

157
00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:46,190
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

158
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,320
♪The stubborn pain♪

159
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:55,980
♪Hardens into the hottest flame♪

160
00:10:58,100 --> 00:11:02,650
♪Taste the fruit you planted,
don't ask me for mercy♪

161
00:11:02,650 --> 00:11:06,090
♪Just enjoy this searing pain♪

162
00:11:06,210 --> 00:11:09,450
♪See whether blood or tears flow first♪

163
00:11:09,580 --> 00:11:12,360
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

164
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:16,770
♪Greed caused the chaos,
none can run away♪

165
00:11:16,770 --> 00:11:20,330
♪The karma you sowed by your own hands♪

166
00:11:20,330 --> 00:11:23,420
♪Watered to maturity
with blood and tears♪

167
00:11:23,670 --> 00:11:26,380
♪Then ignite the anger forged by hatred♪

168
00:11:26,380 --> 00:11:30,590
♪I'll burn it all down♪
